      class  gsEnvironment
      This class is an implementation of the IEnvironment using the graphStream library It currently supports : - 3 types of agents (tanker, explorer and collector), - 1 wumpus (which generates stench), - Well (that generate wind and kill the agents that come in them), - and two types of treasures (gold and diamonds)
